{"tid":2448700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商人到反國安法街站踩場傷區議員女秘書用煙頭燙男秘書 今判囚4周准保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2021-03-16T06:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T06:27:42.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"91d4cf0f612e3617ed646740bf173d0963974a73","tid":2448700,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/YFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FYFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=66219c6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FYFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU%2F&h=b9287597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/YFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議員劉家衡去年5月擺街站反對港區國安法，其間持不同政見的商人到場搗亂，先用煙蒂燙傷劉的男秘書，又出手抓傷區議員李文浩的女秘書。滋事商人早前經審訊後被裁定普通襲擊罪成，暫委裁判官陳姵妏今判刑指，被告向感化官堅持並沒有襲擊事主，考慮到被告沒月悔意、案件涉及的暴力程度、當時社會氛圍撕裂，認為有必要判處監禁式刑罰，且無任何減刑理由，判處被告監禁4星期，但批准他保釋等候上訴。"},{"pid":"39f099609f9a263c898861d48e53f2ff2371bb0b","tid":2448700,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"判咁少仲上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3e600068f95c19ec2368d77eb272939b75d130","tid":2448700,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"換轉係黃打藍就直情無得保釋"},{"pid":"461ee711e86853d6c14b070581e307129817822b","tid":2448700,"uid":56806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"商人 傷人<br />\n有得保釋<br />\n<br />\n商人 辦報<br />\n長期還柙<br />\n<br />\nDLLM極權政府"},{"pid":"f177a82228182d650ba9b80b5d2540aa7ccee9ab","tid":2448700,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"考慮咁多野坐得嗰少少日子，仲未計假期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla